<p>The best part of my job is to see others succeed at pursuing their dreams.</p>

<p>So happy for you, Emile, to move on to your faculty position this fall. We have learnt so much and enjoyed your presence every moment.</p>

<p>I will surely miss you but I am also looking forward to stay in touch. ✨🚀</p>

